headline: Gogo Galileo HDX Coming to Cessna Citation Jet Models
summary: WICHITA, Kan., July 01, 2025--Textron Aviation announced Gogo Galileo HDX will be available for aftermarket installation on Cessna Citation jets after FAA STC expected late 2025.
